metadata.name: VVS Pass
metadata.description:
This is a freemint event to celebrate the launch of the VVS Girls NFT collection.

NO ROADMAP, NO UTILITY

Owning it can bring joy, serve as proof of big fan of the VVS Girls, or become an opportunity to acquire new NFTs. However, the future is uncertain.

The VVS Girls project is planning NFT airdrops, AL distribution, burning redemptions, and exclusive auction events.
